   313                              <1> .no_ret_log:
   314                              <1>     ; Safe return: POP_ALL restores everything.
   315                              <1>     ; Then we must load the transition state WITHOUT clobbering the restored registers.
   316                              <1>     ; We already have the user state in the l3_runtime, but we can't clobber R11/R10
   317                              <1>     ; after popping them.
   318                              <1>     ; SOLUTION: Load them into the stack frame before IRETQ.
   319                              <1>     
