   260                              <1> ; Helper: Select drive and wait for ready
   261                              <1> ; Uses r12d (LBA) for top bits, [ata_drive_sel] for drive
   262                              <1> ; Returns eax=0 success, -1 error
   263                              <1> ata_select_drive:
   264 00003764 6652                <1>     push dx
   265 00003766 6650                <1>     push ax
   266                              <1>     
