  1869                              <1> ; serial_hex32 - Print EAX as 8 hex digits to COM1 (DX = 0x3F8 on entry)
  1870                              <1> ; Clobbers: nothing (saves/restores all used regs)
  1871                              <1> ; ============================================================================
  1872                              <1> serial_hex32:
