    11                              <1> ; Window structure layout (256 bytes per window, qword fields):
    12                              <1> ;   0: ID          8: X           16: Y          24: Width
    13                              <1> ;  32: Height     40: Flags       48: Title (64 bytes inline)
    14                              <1> ; 112: draw_fn   120: key_fn     128: click_fn   136: app_data
    15                              <1> 
    16                              <1> WIN_OFF_ID      equ 0
